    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>In the given sequence of reactions, identify ' $P^{\\prime}, Q^{\\prime}, R^{\\prime}$ and ' $S$ respectively.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m5xacrro/b148064d-5ab7-408a-876b-1b0e8a89e6b9/d8604c50-d2e8-11ef-8c71-155e85fd2e64/file-jaoe38c1m5xacrrp.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m5xacrro/b148064d-5ab7-408a-876b-1b0e8a89e6b9/d8604c50-d2e8-11ef-8c71-155e85fd2e64/file-jaoe38c1m5xacrrp.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2024 Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 8 English\"></p>",
