    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>The alkyl halide required to prepare <img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ltu4r3sg/8bada407-4793-4c8c-887f-b1439fb9453b/fdb84f00-e399-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4r3sh.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ltu4r3sg/8bada407-4793-4c8c-887f-b1439fb9453b/fdb84f00-e399-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4r3sh.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2019 Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 12 English Explanation 1\"> by Wurtz reaction are <img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ltu4rp5a/f3e088a8-6b18-4961-a1fa-182e0e7de2f2/0e37a2e0-e39a-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4rp5b.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ltu4rp5a/f3e088a8-6b18-4961-a1fa-182e0e7de2f2/0e37a2e0-e39a-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4rp5b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2019 Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 12 English Explanation 2\"></p>\n<p>In Wurtz reaction, alkyl halides on treatment with sodium metal in dry ethereal solution give higher alkanes containing even number of carbon atoms.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ltu4srkg/5ba71317-d111-4d96-bf32-5ec07a47a458/2be59900-e39a-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4srkh.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ltu4srkg/5ba71317-d111-4d96-bf32-5ec07a47a458/2be59900-e39a-11ee-ad41-c117e1618884/file-1ltu4srkh.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2019 Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 12 English Explanation 3\"></p>",
