  {
    "comprehension": null,
    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p></p><p>The reagent $X$ used for the following reaction is </p>\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m7hmb1xq/799244bd-d819-4eda-8808-dc12c0306446/7a876ae0-f1e3-11ef-aab0-892656acd133/file-jaoe38c1m7hmb1xr.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m7hmb1xq/799244bd-d819-4eda-8808-dc12c0306446/7a876ae0-f1e3-11ef-aab0-892656acd133/file-jaoe38c1m7hmb1xr.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2018 Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 3 English\">",
