    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<ol start=\"\">\n<p> As, in the given reaction C - C triple bond are changing into $\\mathrm{C}-\\mathrm{C}$ single bond and hydrogen is added. Thus, the given reaction is an example of reduction, which is carried out by $\\mathrm{H}_2$ in the presence of Pd/C catalyst.</p>\n",
